Sentencas: Symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells (S-SOFCs) have received considerable attention due to fewer preparation steps in recent years.
Titulo: Ta-doped PrBaFe2O5 thorn d double perovskite as a high- performance electrode material for symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The PrBaFe2O5+8 (PBF) is a candidate material due to good catalytic activity and electrochemical stability.
Titulo: Ta-doped PrBaFe2O5 thorn d double perovskite as a high- performance electrode material for symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In this work, Ta-substituted PBF materials (PrBaFe2-xTaxO5+8, denoted as PBFTx, x = 0, 0.1, 0.2, 0.3) are prepared and eval-uated as symmetrical electrodes on GDC(Gd0.1Ce0.9O2-8)-YSZ(yttria-stabilized zirconia)-GDC three-layer electrolyte.
Titulo: Ta-doped PrBaFe2O5 thorn d double perovskite as a high- performance electrode material for symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The PrBaFe1.8Ta0.2O5+8 (PBFT0.2) symmetrical cell presents the lowest polarization resistance, and the value is 0.171 U cm2 and 0.503 U cm2 in air and hydrogen atmosphere at 800 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Ta-doped PrBaFe2O5 thorn d double perovskite as a high- performance electrode material for symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In addition, the PBFT0.2 cell shows a peak power density of 234 mW/cm2 using humidified hydrogen as fuel gas and air as oxidant at 800 degrees C, which is enhanced by 68% compared with that of PBF (138 mW/cm2).
Titulo: Ta-doped PrBaFe2O5 thorn d double perovskite as a high- performance electrode material for symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The results indicate that the strategy of Ta doping can improve the electrochemical performance of PBF and PBFT0.2 is a potential electrode for S-SOFCs.(c) 2022
